{"tid":749479,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺有D鬼佬買股票真係好有性格","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:30:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0937c4bca56a4cee635928023854849bc3a157e","tid":749479,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4186032-longer-hold-discover-financial-services\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fseekingalpha.com%2Farticle%2F4186032-longer-hold-discover-financial-services&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w0x4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=8bac3804\" target=\"_blank\">https://seekingalpha.com/article/4186032-longer-hold-discover-financial-services</a><br />\n<br />\n分析到間公司好好 , 但因為間公司贊助過個組織支持墮胎所以要賣左佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fa4PluRo22Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFa4PluRo22Y&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w0x4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=f581c65f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fa4PluRo22Y</a> 8:28開始<br />\n<br />\n覺得軍火商股票不道德所以唔買<br />\n<br />\n全球最大主權基金追求道德投資 禁止向多家企業投資<br />\n2018年01月16日23:33<br />\n<br />\n新浪美股訊 北京時間16日晚，為了追求它所認為的道德投資，擁有11萬億美元資產的挪威主權財富基金週二宣佈禁止向9家新的公司進行投資。<br />\n<br />\n在該基金準備退出其集體投資的公司當中，最知名是英國國防工業企業：英國航空航天系統公司（BAE Systems）。後者在週二通過電子郵件發表聲明稱，BAE公司尊重&ldquo;投資者按照自己的標準作出投資決定的權利&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n代表挪威政府管理運營挪威主權財富基金的挪威中央銀行（Norges Bank）表示，該基金同時還決定不向美國工程企業AECOM、Fluor以及船舶建造商Huntington Ingalls Industries投資。<br />\n<br />\n此前有報導稱，該基金繼續維持對美國企業霍尼韋爾的投資禁令。<br />\n<br />\n挪威中央銀行表示，禁止向上述這些企業投資的原因，是因為所有這些企業均與核武器生產有關。<br />\n<br />\n此外，挪威中央銀行還表示，船運企業長榮海運股份有限公司（Evergreen Marine）、大韓海運（Korea Line）、泰國珍寶航運公司（Precious Shipping）以及泰國泰倫森集團（Thoresen Thai Agencies）被列為禁止投資對象，是因為這些公司的運營存在著&ldquo;重大環境破壞、嚴重或系統性侵犯人權&rdquo;的風險。出於同樣的擔心，韓國泛洋（Pan Ocean）已被列為觀察對象。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭房地產開發商Atal出局，其原因是&ldquo;人權風險&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此前已被挪威主權財富基金列入禁止投資名單的知名企業包括波音、沃爾瑪、菲利普莫里斯以及力拓等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180116/0/2/2/全球最大主權基金追求道德投資-禁止向多家企業投資-8388938.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F0%2F2%2F2%2F%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E5%90%91%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87-8388938.html&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w0x4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=57b9d848\" target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20180116/0/2/2/全球最大主權基金追求道德投資-禁止向多家企業投資-8388938.html</a>[/url]<br />\n<br />\n佢地D信仰真係好堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd2deba5cf454a4021ffd66fde31d2af84b05e0","tid":749479,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"幾個個別姐<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬唔買 咁d股票邊有得升<br />\n<br />\n升就即係有人買"},{"pid":"38053f06652854392161218e04aa8e4233c7d632","tid":749479,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"marketing黎"},{"pid":"83bb2f923cb446c817f55ea9387cdee42da5ee76","tid":749479,"uid":90174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"假膠黎"},{"pid":"8a8909c806ae396158b5c258834238ab35e2962b","tid":749479,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"我曾經都係因為700侵權所以70蚊個陣唔Q買佢.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f24184b3407c80e8067372a718bac0142d0025","tid":749479,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"市場咁多公司，唔買呢幾隻仲有大把選擇，實賺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93269087eb480d87ec0d89f5cdfe565c574ed64b","tid":749479,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8909c806ae396158b5c258834238ab35e2962b","tid":749479,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"cite